        "subject": "LU-5319 client: support multiple modify RPCs in parallel",
        "message": "LU-5319 client: support multiple modify RPCs in parallel\n\nThese patches are the client part of the feature that supports\nmultiple modify RPCs in parallel. Its goal is to improve metadata\noperations performance of a single client, while maintening the\nconsistency of MDT reply reconstruction and MDT recovery mecanisms.\n\nSigned-off-by: Gregoire Pichon <gregoire.pichon@bull.net>\nChange-Id: If345ea1b7b5bb7a3978388b9789181d0fd4de55c\n"
      },
